[01:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'text. It\'s an agent that performs actions. It\'s built on what they call decision intelligence, which is a fancy way of saying it doesn\'t just follow a simple script you'

[01:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'wrote. It understands the intent of your task, dynamically generates a logical plan, and then executes those steps across different platforms. It\'s the difference between telling a'

[02:10] [scene:talk]
